casebody.data:
Alan SAVAGE
v.
Julie Anne ZELENT a/k/a Julie Anne Phillips a/k/a Julie A. McSwain. No. 394P15. Supreme Court of North Carolina. March 17, 2016. Jeffrey S. Miller, Jacksonville, for Zelent, Julie Anne (aka). Daniel G. Cahill, Raleigh, for Savage, Alan. Caroline P. Mackie, Raleigh, for Savage, Alan. Andrew H. Erteschik, Raleigh, for Savage, Alan.

ORDER

Upon consideration of the petition filed on the 24th of November 2015 by Defendant in this matter for discretionary review of the decision of the North Carolina Court of Appeals pursuant to G.S. 7A-31, the following order was entered and is hereby certified to the North Carolina Court of Appeals:

"Denied by order of the Court in conference, this the 17th of March 2016."
